sentence: Рынцәа ириҭаз иеигәырӷьалоит, Рынцәа, урҭ џьаҳанымтәи агәаҟра иацәихьчоит.

sentence: Аллаҳ иҳәатәхамҵара зҽацәызыхьчаз ракәзар, џьанаҭтәи абаҳчақәа рҿы аразҟы иалагәырӷьалоит.

sentence: Ажәаны ишәыҭоу уи амш аҽны, мапкыҩцәа ҳаӷоу имшхара рԥеиԥшуп!

sentence: Абри амшала, уа иҟаз азхаҵаҩцәа алаҳгеит.

sentence: Ҳәарада, агәымбылџьбаҩцәа абри адагьы изықәшәаша даҽа гәаҟрак ыҟоуп, аха реиҳараҩык уи рыздыруам.

sentence: Мамзаргьы дара, Аллаҳ ида даҽа нцәахәык дрымоума? Аллаҳ, урҭ ивадырҟәылақәо зынӡа дырҟәыгоуп.

sentence: Мамзаргьы, шьацҳәак ықәдыргылар рҭахума? Амала ашьацҳәаҵәҟьа иақәшәаша дара азхамҵаҩцәа рхаҭақәа роуп.

sentence: Мамзаргьы, иҟалаша иазку дыррак рыманы, убри анырҵома?

sentence: Ажәҩанқәеи адгьыли дара роума изшаз? Мап! Урҭ иеилкааны иазхазҵо ракәӡам.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Ус анакәха аиаша рҳәозар, уи иашьашәалоу ҳәоук аԥырҵааит!

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Абри, рыхшыҩ ирыднаҵоу, мамзаргьы урҭ иахзырҟьацәаз жәларык ракәу?

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Аха, ибла ацәимгеит, иҳәаагьы дахымсит.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Иҵабыргыҵәҟьаны, уаанӡа данылбаахьазгьы уи дибахьан.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Ибла иабаз, игәгьы мап ацәнамкит.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Убас иҟалеит, иеивагылоу ахәымпалқәа ҩба ирыбжьоу аасҭагьы дизаигәахеит.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Алаԥшҳәаа иахьыҳаракӡаз аҟны дыҟан.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Рыблақәа, ргәыҭҟьара хыланы, рҳаҭгәынқәа ирҭыҵны, арҵуқәа реиԥш иеиԥхьытта анахь, арахь иҩраны иҟоуп.

sentence: Ус анакәха, ааԥхьаҩ, ауаҩы иимбац уи игәыҭҟьагәоу амш ашҟа ааԥхьара аныҟаиҵалак, уаргьы дара урызхьамԥшын.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Изқәыз амҩацәгьа раныхразы урҭ иагьа ажәабжьқәа рызнеихьеит.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Еснагь, имцны иԥхьаӡаны рхатәы ҭахрақәа ирыцныҟәеит. Аха аусқәа зегьы иахьнаӡаша аҭыԥ ыҟоуп.

sentence: Аха уажәшьҭа, Аллаҳ изы асаара шәлаҟәны шәимҵахырхәа!

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Уажәы абри ажәа Аҟәырҟан аума иџьашәшьауа?

sentence: Избанзар иааигәахоит, шәзааигәахара иаҿу амш.

sentence: Убас ишыҟоугьы, Унцәа игәшаҭарақәа узеилымкаакәа, имчразгьы агәыҩбара умоума?

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Хыла-гәыла иаарҳәыз ақалақьқәагьы абас иқәигеит.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD

sentence: Иҟалаша адырра иақәиҭны, убри ала ирбома?

sentence: Аха уи аганахьала дырракгьы рымаӡам, ргәаанагара мацароуп изыцныҟәо. Ҳәарада, агәаанагара адырраҵәҟьа иузадкылом.

sentence: Нарцәы азхазымҵақәо, амаалықьцәа аҳәса рыхьыӡқәа рырҭоит.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Мамзаргы ауаҩы иԥсы иааҭаху зегьы дзырқәиҭхоума?

sentence: Ижәбама урҭ гәыӷырҭада иҟаз Лати, Уззеи?

sentence: Амала, ҳара, уара ушьҭахь ужәлар ԥаҳшәеит, Самариатәи урҭ мҩахиҟьахьеит,- иҳәеит Аллаҳ.

sentence: Аӡәы, хырԥашьа змам уи агәаҟра амш ҵәылхуа дҵааит:- Ианбаҟало?- ҳәа.

sentence: Ус анакәха уи шәиашьапк. Ииашоу амҩа абар, абри ауп.

sentence: Ус ауп, аха ҳарҭ ауааԥсыра ргәы зызҩоз аргәаҟреи, ақәӡаареи узааҳгеит.

sentence: Избанзар, Уи зегьы ҟәыӷарала ирқәиҭу, зегьы здыруа иоуп.

sentence: Уа, Ҳанцәа! аҳәара иҟасҵаз удкыл!

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Избанзар, адгьыл аҟынгьы, ажәҩан аҟынгьы акымзарак Аллаҳ изы имаӡаны изаанхом.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Ҳанцәа! Урҭ рнамаз ииашаны иркырц азы абас ҟасҵеит.

sentence: Уи ишәҭахыз зегьы шәиҭеит.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Аллаҳ ихәыцны аҵатәхәы алырхырц азы ауааԥсыра абас аҿырԥшқәа рзааигоит.

sentence: Урҭ уаҟа иаарҭаху ирқәиҭуп.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Нарцәытәи атәыла акәзар, еиҳагьы ибзиоуп.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Абри адунеи аҟны абзиара ҟазҵаз, алҵшәа бзиа рԥеиԥшуп.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Амҩа иаша шыҟоу еиԥш, ихәахәоу амҩагьы ыҟоуп.

sentence: Амҩа иаша зтәу Аллаҳ иоуп.

sentence: Зжьы шәфо аԥсасеи ашьамаҟеи уи ишеит.

sentence: Уи аҩсҭаа, иахьагьы убас иҟоу ауаа хылаԥшҩыс дрымоуп.

sentence: Аллаҳ иакәзар, иреиҳаӡоу ахьыӡқәа иқәнагоуп.

sentence: Хьаҳәа-ԥаҳәада уи мацара иҳәатәы хаҵатәуп.

sentence: Уи амҩа иаша ианугьы ибзиаӡаны идыруеит.

sentence: Ҳәарада, уара Унцәа имҩахҟьаз зусҭцәоу зегь раасҭа иеиӷьны издыруа иоуп.

sentence: Шәарҭ шәнапаҿы иҟоу нышәхуеит, аха Аллаҳ иҟны иҟоу нҵәара ақәӡам.

sentence: Аллаҳ абри ала шәара шәԥишәоит.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Урҭ уа Аллаҳ ида даҽаӡәы изкӡом.

sentence: Ажәҩан аҵаҟа Аллаҳ идҵа аҿаԥхьа ихырхәаны иԥыруа аԥсаатә рымбаӡои?

sentence: Ҳәарада, Аллаҳ зегьы имч рықәхоит.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Ҳәарада, Аллаҳ адырреи амчреи дрықәиҭуп.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Шәарҭ Аллаҳ шәишеит, нас шәыԥсы шәхихраны дыҟоуп.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Урҭ урмаӷьлан! Рҩыџьагьы ргәы ҟазҵаша ажәақәа раҳәала.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Урҭ рыбжьара руаӡәы, мамзагьы рҩыџьагьы, рықәрахь ианнеилак, уф! ҳәаҵәҟьа роумҳәан!

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Шәыгәқәа ирҭоу зегьы, ибзиаӡаны издыруа шәынцәа иоуп.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Уара аԥсы иазкны азҵаара урҭоит.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Ауаҩԥсы, абзиара кырӡа пату ақәзымҵо иоуп!

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Шәарҭ зегьы шәаасҭа еиӷьны шәыздыруа шәынцәа иоуп.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Нас, рԥаҵа иалаччаны рхы аарҵысны иҵаахуеит:- Ианбыкәу уи аныҟало?- ҳәа.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Ҳәарада, Уи иуааԥсыра зҿу идыруеит, урҭ зегьы ишахәҭоу ибоит.

sentence: Уи убас ибзианы ибоит, убасгьы ибзианы иаҳауеит, уаҳа ҟалашьа амам!

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Дара ирызкны адырра змоу шьарда имаҷҩуп.

sentence: Рнапхгара ракәзар, иеицҿакны ирҳәеит:- Ҳара урҭ рывараҿы хымԥада ныҳәарҭак ҳаргылоит.

sentence: Урҭ рыхьӡала баҟак шәыргыл рҳәеит.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Шаҟа аамҭа шәыцәаз?- ҳәа руаӡәк дҵааит.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Мамзар, зынӡа ииашамыз акы ҟаҳҵон.

sentence: Ихьӡқәа ишәҳәалак ҟалоит, избанзар иԥшӡоу ахьӡқәа зегьы иара мацара изкуп.

sentence: Абар, Исраил иԥацәа уразҵаа.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Ауаҩыԥсы инапы даараӡа икуп.

sentence: Аллаҳ имч, зегьы ишахәҭоу ала ирызхоит.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Абри аҩыза ахлымӡаах аамҭазгьы ацхыраара ахьҳауа Аллаҳ иҟынтә ауп.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Саргьы, сынцәа, уара уқәаҵа аасҭа иеиӷьу сиҭап ҳәа сгәыӷуеит.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Шаҟа иҳамҭа бзиоузеи, шаҟагьы нхарҭа бзиоузеи!

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Убарҭ рзы, зыҩныҵҟа аӡиасқәа зҭысуа Аднтәи џьанаҭқәа ыҟоуп.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Шаҟа рыжәтә бааԥсузеи уи, шаҟа нхарҭа бааԥсузеи уи аҭыԥ!

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Аҵабырг, шәынцәа иҟынтә иааиз ауп.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Уи илԥха роурц азы уахгьы ҽынгьы иҳәара иаҿу ауаа урыцларц азы ухандеи.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Иҟоу зегьы Аллаҳ ида напхгаҩы дрымаӡам.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Бара ибызкны иӡбоу абри ауп,- иҳәеит амаалықь.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Ус ишыҟаз, Иаҳиа диит, деизҳаит.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Уа, Анцәа! Иаарту дыргак сырба,- иҳәеит Зеқьериа.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Иагьа ус иҟазаргьы, уи сара сзы имариоуп, уара ухаҭагьы уаанӡа уаныҟамыз усшахьан.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Сынцәа!- иҳәеит,- Сара сыбаҩқәа кәадахеит, схы шлеит.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Уи маӡала инцәа диҳәеит.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Сара, шәара шәеиԥш суаҩԥсы мацароуп.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Урҭ уа наунагӡа инхараны иҟоуп.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Амала сынцәа иажәа аҽҳәара анааилак, абри ицҟьа иқәиҵоит.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Сара, аиха рацәа сзаажәг.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Аҳра иара мацара итәуп, насгьы арҽхәаԥхьыӡқәа зегьы иара изкуп.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Аллаҳ иҭахымкәа, рыцҳарак шәақәшәараны шәыҟаӡам.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Дарбанзаалак, Аллаҳ иҳәаа дахысыр, ихы арыцҳара иҭаиргылоит.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Уигьы мҩак дықәлеит.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Аҭӡамц аҵаҟагьы дара иртәны ахьы хәыҵан, рабгьы дуаҩԥсы бзиан.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Аҭӡамц атәы уҳәозар, уи ахыбра, ҩыџьа аиеҭым хәыҷқәа иртәын.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Икылжәаны грак асҭеит.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Уи аӷба ҳзықәтәаз, амшын аҟны аус зуаз уаа ӷарқәак иртәын.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Иуҭаххар уџьабаа ахәԥса рымхра улшон,- иҳәеит Мыса.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Ишнеиуаз, қыҭак иналаланы ауаа рҟынтә афатә иаҳәеит.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Ҳәарада, Аллаҳ саргьы сынцәа иоуп, шәаргьы шәынцәа иоуп.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Уи акы аниӡбо,уҟала! ҳәа аҳәара мацара азхоит, иаразнак иааҟалоит.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Уи адагьы, сан лаҳаҭыр абара сыдиҵеит, сара қәымчҩыс, ҿагылаҩыс сҟаимҵеит.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Араҟа уара узы амлакреи, маҭәада анхареи ҳәа акагьы ыҟаӡам.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Уи амшалагьы, аарлаҳәа иуаҳауа быжьқәак рыда улымҳа акгьы ҭаҩӡом.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Уи амш аҽны, зегьы рааԥхьаҩы Исрафил ицныҟәоит.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Уигьы убас аҭак ҟаиҵеит: Уа сан лԥа! сыхцәы, сжакьа уамыхан.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Ари ауаҩы, убарҭ ахьқәа рҭәаны, ихәаауаз ҳәыск абаҟа ҟаиҵеит.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Сара агәаԥхара уоурц азы сыццакны сузааит.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Уа Сынцәа! Абар, даргьы сара сышьҭа ихуп.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Уажәшьҭа уара иуҭаху, ишыуҭаху, иӡбала, амала уара уӡбарақәа ари адунеи мацара иазкхоит.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Мап, раԥхьа шәара ишәыршә,- иҳәеит Мыса.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Уажәшьҭа Исраил иԥацәа рхы иазоужь, иҳацны иааиааит.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Фараон шәизца, избанзар уи аҳәаа кырӡа дахысит.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Абас ала, сылаԥш ухны урааӡап, уеизҳап ҳәа.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Уара убаны, уздыруа рыгәқәа рҿы, уара узы бзиабарак ҭасҵеит.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Уа Мыса! Уарӷьа напы иаку закәызеи?

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Сара сыда Нцәа дыҟам.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Аллаҳ амҩа иаша иану рылашара ирӷәӷәоит.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Ус анакәха, ичҳаны, умхьаҵкәа иара иҳәатәы хаҵа.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Уара Унцәа зынӡа хашҭра зқәу иакәӡам.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Иара убас, аӡбагьы уакуам, ашоурагьы.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Нас, урҭ ираҳҭаз ҳажәа наҳагӡеит.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Сара сынцәа, дгьыли жәҩани рҿы иеибырҳәо зегьы идыруеит.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Зегьы ԥшуп, ус анакәха, шәаргьы шәыԥшыз,- убас ҳәа.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Уара уҟынтә аразҟы ҳҭахым, ҳара ҳоуп аразҟы узҭо.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Аҵыхәтәан, рҩыџьагьы уи аҵла аҟынтә аҵәа рфеит.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Насгьы, иазыԥҵәоу аамҭазы, Аллаҳ разҟыс ириҭаз, аӡатәқәа уи ихьӡ ҳәаны иршьырц азы иааиааит.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Аллаҳ илаирҟәыз ауаҩы дҳаразкуа аӡәгьы дзыҟалом.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Ҳәарада, Аллаҳ зегьы ишахәҭоу ала шаҳаҭра рзиуеит.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Ҳәарада, Аллаҳ ишиҭаху иҟаиҵоит.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Абас алагьы, ҳамчра шәҳарбоит.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Зцәа зтәымкәа иҟоу аҳәса ироураны иҟоу рыхшара рцәыӡуеит.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Уи ада уаҳа бжьыкгьы раҳауам.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD

sentence: Урҭ абри адагьы, иага аус цәгьақәа нарыгӡоит.

sentence: Ишәфо ифоит, ишәжәуа ижәуеит.

sentence: Закәытә ҵыхәтәа цәгьоузеи уи!

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Ҳажәа ԥҟарақәа ирзаԥхьо ауаа ирыжәларц азы ак рыгхом.

sentence: Ҳәарада, идуӡӡоу, иҳаракӡоу Аллаҳ имацара иоуп.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD

sentence: Абри аҩыза ахара адҵаразы, ԥшьҩык ашаҳаҭцәа ааргааит.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Амала аҭамзаара шьҭаҵаны зхы зыриашаз ракәзар, уахь иалаӡам.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Уи ида нцәа дыҟаӡам.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Алашара инахыкны даҽа лашарак ахылҵуеит.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Ааи, абас ауп.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Унцәа зегьы ишахәҭоу ала избо иоуп.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Илашәу, ицыркьу, насгьы ичмазаҩу рзы игәырԥсам.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Аллаҳ изаҳауеи, издыруеи иоуп.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Баша шәымқәын, аҳәатәы шхашәҵо иеилкаауп! Аллаҳ иҟашәҵо зегьы идыруеит.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Аллаҳ ииҭаху ишоит, ҳәарада Аллаҳ зегьы дрықәиҭуп.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Аллаҳ ԥсы зхо зегьы аӡы иалихит.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Иумбаӡои? Аллаҳ аԥҭақәа ирныҟәоит, нас иеидиҵоит, насгьы урҭ иеиқәҵаны ижәпаӡоу ԥҭақәаны иҟаиҵоит.

sentence: Аҵыхәтәан, уи аҭыԥаҿы даннеилак, акгьы избом, аха Аллаҳ ивараҿы дибоит.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD

sentence: Уи аразҟы шәызҭо иреиӷьӡоу иоуп.

sentence: Ҳәарада, абарҭқәа Аллаҳ изы даараӡа имариоуп.

sentence: Уажәы уи дыжәбар шәҭахума?

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD

sentence: Урҭ раԥхьаӡа изшаз иоуп аԥсы рхазҵо,- убас ҳәа.

sentence: Аллаҳ хаҵеи-ԥҳәыси иеилыхны, аҭыԥҳацәа роума иалихыз?

sentence: Уаԥсҵәык аҵиаа аашьҭыхны, убри ала уԥҳәыс улыс, абас ала уажәагьы наугӡап,- ҳҳәеит.

sentence: Исанажь, сара снаҩс уаҳа аӡәгьы имоуша аҳрак саҭәашьа.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Абас ишыҟоугьы, уигьы сара исыҭ ҳәа сыхҭаикит.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Абри ауаҩ, сашьа иоуп.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Аллаҳ иуааԥсыра гәаҟрак иақәшәар иҭахым.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Ҳәарада, Аллаҳ зегьы ибзиаӡаны изаҳауа, избо иоуп.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Насгьы Аллаҳ зегьы ииашаны иӡбоит.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Уи аҽны, зегьы иҟарҵаз ацымхәра роуеит.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Хымԥада, иаӡәу, насгьы хьаҳәа-ԥаҳәада аҳра иақәиҭу Аллаҳ иоуп.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Иахьа аҳра зтәыда?

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Амала, Аллаҳ иахь зхы хоу ида, абри аӡәгьы ҵатәхәык изалхуам.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Уажәшьҭа уи аӡбара аус, иҳаракӡоу Аллаҳ итәуп.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Уа, Ҳанцәа! Ҳарҭ, ҩынтә ҳаԥсы ҳхухит, ҩынтәгьы ҳаԥсы ҳхауҵеит.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Уинахыс, Унцәа илшарала адгьыл лашоит.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Ахашшаара зегь рыла Аллаҳ итәуп.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Имԥсызгьы дшыцәоу иԥсы ихихуеит.

sentence: Акаамеҭ аныҟало аамҭа Аллаҳ имацара иоуп издыруа.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Уара Унцәа, иуааԥсыра аиашамра рзиуӡом.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Абас ишыҟоугьы, иҵаулаӡоу гәыҩбарак рызцәырҵит.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Уи аԥсы ахазҵо, хымԥада, аԥсцәагьы иргылоит.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Аҵхи амши, амреи амзеи, уи идыргақәа иреиуоуп.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Абзиареи ацәгьареи акны изыҟалом.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Дара амҩа иаша абара аасҭа, алашәра мҩас иалырхит.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Семуд жәлар ракәзар, урҭгьы амҩа иаша дҳарбеит.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Ус анакәха, ҳарҭ уара ула иаашьҭу, иҵабыргны иҳазхаҵом,- рҳәеит.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Ҳара, иааигәоу ажәҩан, ацәашьқәа рыла аеҵәақәа рыла иҳархиеит, насгьы иҳахьчеит.

sentence: Иаҳҭахны ҳааит ҳәа аҭак ҟарҵеит.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Абарҭқәа зегьы ԥшьаамҭак рыла иаԥиҵеит.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Уажәшьҭа шәышиашоу иара иахь шәхы шәырха, уи иҟынтә анажьра шәаҳәа.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Сара Анцәа дшаӡәу сыҵаҳәоуп.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Саргьы шәара шәеиԥш уаҩԥсык соуп.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Уареи ҳареи ҳабжьара ԥардак ҳабжьоуп.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Ҳара, ааԥхьара иҳауҭаз азы ҳагәқәа аркуп, ҳлымҳақәа дагәоуп.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Аллаҳ иуааԥсыра ирызкны ажәытә аахыс имҩаԥиго иԥҟара абас ауп ишыҟоу.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Ажәакала, ҽҳәарак аҟынӡа шәыԥсы ҭаны шәынзырхо иара иоуп.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Уи еснагь дыбзоуп, иара ида нцәа дыҟам.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Уи ида нцәа дыҟам.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Убас ауп дшыҟоу шәара ишәынцәоу Аллаҳ.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Ҳәарада, зегьы заҳауа, насгьы зегьы збо иара имацара иоуп.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Ус анакәха, уара Аллаҳ уҽимада.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Ҳәарада, уи зуааԥсыра бзиа избо, изыхьчо иоуп.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Сара сус Аллаҳ инапы ианысҵоит.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Аиашазы, шәарҭ, абри адунеи азгьы, нарцәы азгьы, иаԥсам ааԥхьарак сышәҭоит.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Фараон ишьацҳәа зынӡа лыҵшәада иаанхеит.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Абас ала, Фараон иҟаиҵаз ахәымгара ибзиоушәа ирбаны, амҩа иаша дахырҟьеит.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Аҭәашьара дуӡӡагьы абар абри ауп.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Урҭ рзы рынцәа иҿаԥхьа иаарҭаху зегьы ыҟоуп.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Амала уи нарцәытәи аразҟы ҳәа акгьы иоуӡом.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Шәареи ҳареи ҳабжьара аимак аҭахӡам.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Иара убри амшала, уааԥхьара ушаҿыц уаҿыз, насгьы ишуыдҵо еиԥш уиашара иацҵа.

sentence: Иара иахь зхы хоугьы аиашахь икылигоит.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Аллаҳ ииҭаху ԥааимбарс далихуеит.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Избанзар, уи зегьы здыруа иоуп.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Уи изаҳауа иоуп, избо иоуп.

sentence: Уи иеиԥшу дыҟаӡам.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Абас ала шәеизҳара алиршоит.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Уи зегьы имч ақәхоит.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
sentence: Аԥсцәагьы зыргыло уи иоуп.

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD

source: I have permission from the translator, https://github.com/danielinux7/Abkhazian-books-in-Public-Domain/tree/master/%D0%90%D2%9F%D3%99%D1%8B%D1%80%D2%9F%D0%B0%D0%BD
